This is my 7th map. 
And this map has Cell Shaded Effect :D
Hopefully its good enough. :D
I made it in 5 hours and came out pretty well! :]
Gun Game. Lots of places to hide. in the darkness. 
Creep up to ur enemies :]

I really hope you all like this map. even though it was fast to make.
I really tried my best :].

Btw. LOST. Comment/Rate the map :D

Thank you everyone.

"INSTALL NOTES"
place the 'gg_cl1_asylum.bsp file
in your Maps folder usualy located in.

C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\ - - your account - - \counter-strike source\cstrike\maps
